{"tid":990750,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"聖卡斯玩「10年挑戰」得罪老婆","createTime":"2019-01-22T00:57:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T05:33:04.000Z","uid":153600,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"faf32c8f2e376c75e925d1b99a7e8a7455e5156b","tid":990750,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T00:57:45.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=Wqf%2BBtIb0uKZLQ16pRiKQW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=2e467c1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】「10年挑戰」最近紅遍網絡，傳奇門將卡斯拿斯也湊熱鬧，想不到竟然得罪了太太！<br />\n<br />\n37歲的卡斯拿斯（Iker Casillas）成為最新一名參與「10年挑戰」的足球員，在Instagram上載了跟太太Sara Carbonero的10年前相片；當時兩人到西班牙小鎮Navalacruz旅遊。<br />\n<br />\n不過，Sara似乎不太喜歡丈夫上載這張相片，未知是否因為不滿意自己在相中的樣貌或衣著；她在相片留了兩個簡單的emoji，但肯定會令卡斯拿斯心驚膽戰，就是一個水槍、一個骷髏頭！<br />\n<br />\n聖卡斯跟Sara耍花槍，在波圖亦和得十分開心，更表示在退役後肯定會再次回到葡萄：「我希望回來看比賽，最好是對皇家馬德里。」他更大讚波圖球迷：「當我們主場被利物浦炒5蛋，球迷仍然拍掌，完全沒有喝倒彩。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6649a83bd3395952780df32f5a3e97d09744d760","tid":990750,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T00:58:45.000Z","msg":"圖呢？"},{"pid":"5acc807bab2048df4a34e2bd44288a0e5763330e","tid":990750,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:00:45.000Z","msg":"更表示在退役後肯定會再次回到葡萄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb4cbc93d274d687491262665ad1a1882c2503b","tid":990750,"uid":45772,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:06:26.000Z","msg":"當我們主場被利物浦炒5蛋，球迷仍然拍掌，完全沒有喝倒彩。」<br />\n利記又贏"},{"pid":"58b6cafbeebdc5b83ca74f82be860450c9c4d9ed","tid":990750,"uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:08:03.000Z","msg":"死毒撚真係好恐怖<br />\n咁都ff人唔鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af55894548a62bf34e27881ef5d6bc765997d37c","tid":990750,"uid":203961,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4bb4cbc93d274d687491262665ad1a1882c2503b","tid":990750,"uid":45772,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:06:26.000Z","msg":"當我們主場被利物浦炒5蛋，球迷仍然拍掌，完全沒有喝倒彩。」<br />\n利記又贏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:13:56.000Z","msg":"係皇馬的時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42addf8274b18e2cfc65ee356d6119a715ef57e0","tid":990750,"uid":171754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:14:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"688d5478a5bcaa3979d0de355b57e67fdf0cbad1","tid":990750,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:16:02.000Z","msg":"個樣都冇咩變"},{"pid":"084709dcdeee3058e4ff510c5e9a1c7316052a31","tid":990750,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:33:04.000Z","msg":"水槍係叫聖卡今晚射佢咋"}]}